Package com.test.pool

Interface Summary
BlockingPool<T> Represents a pool of objects that makes the requesting threads wait if no object is available.
ObjectFactory<T> Represents the mechanism to create new objects to be used in an object pool.
Pool<T> Represents a cached pool of objects.
Pool.Validator<T> Represents the functionality to validate an object of the pool and to subsequently perform cleanup activities.
 

Class Summary
PoolFactory Factory and utility methods for Pool and BlockingPool classes defined in this package.
